title: #133: The Far Side Of The Moon With Jamey Jasta
description:
Thank you for tuning for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam welcomes from the Jasta Show and Hatebreed, Jamey Jasta, to talk the far side of the Moon. This episode is crazy. I have to honest I didn't have time to do as much research as I normally do so we kind of just wing. We discuss....
1) We talk podcasting and touring
2)Hollow Moon:
3)Annunaki
4) NASA and Black Ops
5)The Shard and The Tower
6) Aaron ruins everything
Thanks for listening. Thank you Marc Harde for helping do research for the show. Please check out our sponsors BETDSI.com and use the promo code Hat100.
